{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"12bbe487da","title":"在达赖、班禅为庆祝藏历木羊年新年举行的宴会上的祝酒词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e4746833b2","index":0,"year":1955,"month":2,"day":24,"articleId":"12bbe487da"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"683c894ef6","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"12bbe487da","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"达赖，即达赖喇嘛·丹增嘉措，当时任全国人大常委会副委员长。班禅，即班禅额尔德尼·确吉坚赞，当时任政协全国委员会副主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"efd9aa907a","type":"title","text":"在达赖、班禅叫为庆祝藏历木羊年新年举行的宴会上的祝酒词","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"12bbe487da"},{"id":"683c894ef6","type":"paragraph","text":"达赖喇嘛、班禅额尔德尼、各位先生、各位同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"12bbe487da"},{"id":"0e382fe0ef","type":"paragraph","text":"当看藏族新年的时候，让我们尚达赖喇嘛、班禅额尔德尼祝贺，向西藏全体在京人员祝贺，向西藏和其他地区的全体藏族人民祝贺！我们天家应当努力，进一步加强和巩固我国各民族间的团结，进一步加强和巩固汉、藏民族间以及藏族内部的团结，共同建设我们伟大的祖国。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"12bbe487da"},{"id":"1ddc42e453","type":"paragraph","text":"让我们为达赖喇嘛、班禅额尔德尼的健康，为西藏全体在京借俗人员的健康，为我国民族的大团结而干杯！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"12bbe487da"}],"page":{"id":"6068738f8f","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"12bbe487da","start":471,"end":471}}}},"__N_SSG":true}